title: #92Noon! Montage/Birk/Siny/Bercich/Lavelle
description: Sad montage to start following a border battle loss, Matt Birk and Dave Sinykin both join during first hour, Pete Bercich in the mix for most of the 10a hour, then football talkers thru to a Lavelle cold-call at the end of the show!
